==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Barm
<hw>Barm</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[OE. <ets>bearm</ets>,
<ets>berm</ets>, <ets>barm</ets>, AS. <ets>bearm</ets>; akin to E.
<ets>bear</ets> to support.]</ety> <def>The lap or bosom.</def>
